statements.sql: select `page_tbls`.*, `permissions`.`user_id` as `pivot_user_id`, `permissions`.`page_id` as `pivot_page_id` from `page_tbls` inner join `permissions` on `page_tbls`.`id` = `permissions`.`page_id` where `permissions`.`user_id` in (1)

select count(*) as aggregate from `assessments_tbls` left join `students_tbls` on `assessments_tbls`.`student_id` = `students_tbls`.`id` left join `enrollment_tbls` on `assessments_tbls`.`enrollment_id` = `enrollment_tbls`.`id` left join `branch_tbls` on `enrollment_tbls`.`branch_id` = `branch_tbls`.`id` left join `curriculum_tbls` on `enrollment_tbls`.`curriculum_id` = `curriculum_tbls`.`id` left join `program_majors_tbls` on `curriculum_tbls`.`program_major_id` = `program_majors_tbls`.`id`

select count(*) as aggregate from `assessments_tbls` left join `students_tbls` on `assessments_tbls`.`student_id` = `students_tbls`.`id` left join `enrollment_tbls` on `assessments_tbls`.`enrollment_id` = `enrollment_tbls`.`id` left join `branch_tbls` on `enrollment_tbls`.`branch_id` = `branch_tbls`.`id` left join `curriculum_tbls` on `enrollment_tbls`.`curriculum_id` = `curriculum_tbls`.`id` left join `program_majors_tbls` on `curriculum_tbls`.`program_major_id` = `program_majors_tbls`.`id` where (LOWER(`branch_tbls`.`branch_name`) LIKE '%kevi%' or LOWER(`enrollment_tbls`.`application_no`) LIKE '%kevi%' or (`last_name` like '%kevi%' or `first_name` like '%kevi%' or `middle_name` like '%kevi%') or LOWER(`assessments_tbls`.`fee_amount`) LIKE '%kevi%' or LOWER(`assessments_tbls`.`student_department`) LIKE '%kevi%' or LOWER(`program_majors_tbls`.`description`) LIKE '%kevi%' or LOWER(`assessments_tbls`.`status`) LIKE '%kevi%')

select `assessments_tbls`.*, `students_tbls`.`first_name`, `students_tbls`.`middle_name`, `students_tbls`.`last_name`, `enrollment_tbls`.`application_no`, `enrollment_tbls`.`subject_ids` as `subject_ids`, `branch_tbls`.`branch_name`, `program_majors_tbls`.`description`, (select sum(`payment_history_tbls`.`payment_amount`) from `payment_history_tbls` where `assessments_tbls`.`id` = `payment_history_tbls`.`assessments_id`) as `total_payment_amount` from `assessments_tbls` left join `students_tbls` on `assessments_tbls`.`student_id` = `students_tbls`.`id` left join `enrollment_tbls` on `assessments_tbls`.`enrollment_id` = `enrollment_tbls`.`id` left join `branch_tbls` on `enrollment_tbls`.`branch_id` = `branch_tbls`.`id` left join `curriculum_tbls` on `enrollment_tbls`.`curriculum_id` = `curriculum_tbls`.`id` left join `program_majors_tbls` on `curriculum_tbls`.`program_major_id` = `program_majors_tbls`.`id` where (LOWER(`branch_tbls`.`branch_name`) LIKE '%kevi%' or LOWER(`enrollment_tbls`.`application_no`) LIKE '%kevi%' or (`last_name` like '%kevi%' or `first_name` like '%kevi%' or `middle_name` like '%kevi%') or LOWER(`assessments_tbls`.`fee_amount`) LIKE '%kevi%' or LOWER(`assessments_tbls`.`student_department`) LIKE '%kevi%' or LOWER(`program_majors_tbls`.`description`) LIKE '%kevi%' or LOWER(`assessments_tbls`.`status`) LIKE '%kevi%') limit 10 offset 0
